author_ssm: Laura Newsome, 2011. Accretions processed by Nicholas Martin, 2014.
abstract_ssm: William Anthony (1934-2022) was an American painter, illustrator, and graphic artist working in satire. This William Anthony Papers primarily contain facsimiles of Anthony's work, documenting his artistic career from 1976 though 2004. There are also some original artworks, photographs of Anthony, and other personal materials.
